episodes.title: Take Your Little Gun and Get Out of My Trailer Park
episodes.plot: After spending 18 months in jail, Sunnyvale's Ricky and Julian head home, looking to get things back on track. But when they return, a bully has taken control of their beloved park.

episodes.title: Fuck Community College. Let's Get Drunk and Eat Chicken Fingers
episodes.plot: Julian decides it's time he left Sunnyvale Trailer Park and actually do something productive with his life and chooses to go to a community college.

episodes.title: Mr. Lahey's Got My Porno Tape!
episodes.plot: Ricky and Bubbles both agree to star in J-Roc's new porn, but Ricky can't go through with it, forcing Bubbles to take his place in a real steamy scene.

episodes.title: Mrs. Peterson's Dog Gets Fucked Up
episodes.plot: Ricky lets a dog eat a tray of hash brownies and has to take it to the veterinarian. He must then run errands for the vet to pay for it.

episodes.title: I'm Not Gay, I love Lucy. Wait a Second, Maybe I am Gay
episodes.plot: Julian decides to get Ricky to marry Lucy so they'll both get off his back. He goes with Ricky to get a ring (by breaking into a house) and to get him a job (by asking Levi).

episodes.title: Who the Hell Invited These Idiots to My Wedding?
episodes.plot: Lucy asks Julian to plan the wedding because she thinks Ricky is not up to it, but his plans cause the cops to show up and ruin the wedding.
